sources.description:
A college dropout convinces his family to re-examine his goals and gets them to leave it all for a cross-country odyssey in a 1928 Greyhound bus.

Director: Paul Bogart
Writer: Lewis John Carlino
Stars: Jeff Bridges, Carl Betz, Vera Miles, Ruth McDevitt
Genres: Drama
